sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI as CLI<br/>(bin/nemoclaw.js)
    participant Onboard as Onboarding Wizard<br/>(bin/lib/onboard.js)
    participant Preflight as Preflight Checks<br/>(bin/lib/preflight.js)
    participant Blueprint as Blueprint Runner<br/>(nemoclaw-blueprint/)
    participant Gateway as OpenShell Gateway
    participant Sandbox as Sandbox Container
    participant Inference as Inference API

    User->>CLI: nemoclaw onboard --profile vllm
    CLI->>Onboard: Start onboarding wizard
    
    Note over Onboard: Interactive configuration
    Onboard->>Onboard: Select inference profile
    Onboard->>Onboard: Configure GPU (optional)
    Onboard->>Onboard: Select model
    
    Onboard->>Preflight: Run preflight checks
    
    Note over Preflight: System validation
    Preflight->>Preflight: Check OpenShell installed
    Preflight->>Preflight: Check Docker running
    Preflight->>Preflight: Check GPU availability
    Preflight->>Preflight: Verify credentials
    Preflight-->>Onboard: ✅ All checks passed
    
    Onboard->>Blueprint: Execute blueprint
    
    Note over Blueprint: Orchestration lifecycle
    Blueprint->>Blueprint: Resolve blueprint version
    Blueprint->>Blueprint: Verify artifact digest
    Blueprint->>Blueprint: Generate execution plan
    Blueprint->>Blueprint: Apply plan
    
    Blueprint->>Gateway: Deploy sandbox
    Gateway->>Sandbox: Create container
    Gateway->>Sandbox: Apply network policy
    Gateway->>Sandbox: Mount volumes
    Sandbox-->>Gateway: Container ready
    Gateway-->>Blueprint: Sandbox deployed
    
    Blueprint->>Gateway: Configure inference routing
    Gateway->>Inference: Test connection
    Inference-->>Gateway: Connection OK
    Gateway-->>Blueprint: Routing configured
    
    Blueprint-->>Onboard: Deployment complete
    Onboard-->>CLI: Success with sandbox details
    CLI-->>User: ✅ Sandbox ready!<br/>Name: openclaw-sandbox-vllm<br/>Model: llama-3.1-8b
